<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>śākābdānāṁ tu gaṇi
<lb n="2" break="no"/>tē vyōmabhūśaśisōma
<lb n="3" break="no"/>kē<supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> saumyavārē tu paṁ
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ccamyāṁ śuklē caitrasya
<lb n="5"/>pakṣakē <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> kollūrākhyē pu
<lb n="6" break="no"/>rā grāmē prābhūdeṟapadē
<lb n="7" break="no"/>saṭiḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> tatputrō ghaḍyanō nā
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ma gōṁkkabhūpacamūpatiḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
<lb n="9"/>tatputraḥ kuladugdhābdhiva
<lb n="10" break="no"/>rddhanē pūrnnacaṁcramāḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> ku
<lb n="11" break="no"/>lōttuṁggāṁkavīrasya pri
<lb n="12" break="no"/>dhvīśasya camūpatiḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> Ā
<lb n="13" break="no"/>dau bhaṭagaṇēgaṇya<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> śrīmā
<lb n="14" break="no"/>neṟapanāyakaḥ<supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> varttē
<lb n="15" break="no"/>tē yāvadindvarkkau tāva
<lb n="16" break="no"/>tkāliṁggadēśakē <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> pituru
<lb n="17"/>ddiśya dharmmārtthaṁ prādāddī
<lb n="18" break="no"/>pamakhaṁḍakaṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> A
<lb n="19" break="no"/>smai śrīkūrmmanādhāya
<lb n="20"/>pūrnnakōṭinivāsinē <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>
<lb n="21"/>Ī dīpamu naḍapa
<lb n="22"/>śrīkūrmmamū
<lb n="23" break="no"/>na gollasūrabō
<lb n="24" break="no"/>yuni vasamuna
<lb n="25" break="no"/>ṁbeṭṭina goṟiya 50 <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> 
</p>

